  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Levi Log Cabins are self-catered cabins. Each cabin has an equipped kitchen, and the supermarket is in the centre of resort. There is also the option to pre-book half board meals, which can be added on when booking a Levi Log Cabin. Breakfast and dinner will be served at the Sirkantähti Hotel, which is around a 5 minute walk (400m) away.</p>
<p>A buffet style breakfast is served in the main hotel restaurant each morning, with a great selection of sweet and savoury options including a continental breakfast with additional daily hot options.  Each evening you'll have a three course buffet dinner in the Sirkantähti Restaurant, which includes meat and vegetarian options, plus a salad bar.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music. Please also note that the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
