  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Levi Log Cabins are in a quiet and scenic wooded location, however they are nearby to the <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a> centre. Each cabin is built and furnished in a traditional style, with all the modern amenities needed for you holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a>. </p>
<h2>Scenic location</h2>
<p><span>Nestled amidst the snow-covered landscape of Levi, you'll find the charming Levi Log Cabins. These cosy cabins </span>benefit from being in a secluded wooded area set back from the main village. The centre of Levi is only a five minute walk away, where you can find a range of gift shops, cosy cafes and restaurants, as well as a well stocked supermarket. </p>
<p><span>Outside, a world of wonders awaits. Our optional extra <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">excursions</a> are an excellent way to explore the wilderness and give you a better chance of spotting the Northern Lights. Whizz through the untouched snowy landscape on snowmobile, enjoy a serene sleighride led by a reindeer or mush your way through the frozen forests on a husky excursion. </span></p>
<h2>Cosy log cabins</h2>
<p>Enjoy a cosy Christmas break this year in traditional log cabin, surrounded by a wooded area just a short walk from the village centre, these round wood cabins are just what you imagine when you think of <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a>. The cabins provide a cosy haven for your Christmas break, furnished in a traditional Lappish style. Warm up in front of the fireplace in the lounge area or embrace Finnish traditions and enjoy relaxing in your own private sauna included in each cabin. <span>Enjoy the snowy settings from your cabin, with the mystical Northern Lights often painting the night sky with hues of emerald, violet, and sapphire.</span> We have a choice of different cabins, ideal for a group of friends or a family who are after their own private space in traditional accommodation in Lapland. </p>
<h2>Eat in or dine out</h2>
<p>The Levi Log cabins are offered on a self-catering board basis, the cabins have a fully equipped kitchen with a range of appliances and the well-stocked supermarket is just a short walk away. Take the fuss out of meal times and pre-book the optional half-board taken at the <a data-udi="umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52b14671f33a4004bfb62c7f25c5b1cf}" title="Sirkantahti Hotel">Sirkantähti Hotel,</a> which is around a 5 minute walk (400m) from the cabins. Each day you can enjoy a buffet style breakfast with a great selection of sweet and savoury options including a continental breakfast with additional daily hot options.  Dinner is served buffet style at the Sirkantähti Restaurant, where you will have a choice of main courses and a daily salad buffet. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
