  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Lomailevi C7</strong> cabins are terraced and are around around 57m<sup>2 </sup>sleeping two to six people. These cabins are set over two levels and have one double bedroom downstairs and four single beds in the mezzanine area. These cabins also have Wi-Fi access.</p>
<p><strong>Lomailevi D13 </strong>cabins are terrace and are around 57m<sup>2 </sup> sleeping two to six people. These cabins are set over two levels and have one double bedroom downstairs and four single beds in the mezzanine area. <sup>  </sup></p>
<p><strong>Nilijoutsen B8 </strong>cabins are terraced, and are around 95m<sup>2 </sup>sleeping for to eight people. The cabin has three twin bedrooms downstairs, and two single beds in the mezzanine area. There are two toilets in the cabins.</p>
<p><strong>Nilijoutsen A3 </strong>cabins are semi-detached, and are around 87m<sup>2</sup> sleeping two to six people. The cabin has one double bedroom, and four single beds There are two toilets in the cabins. </p>
<p><strong>Nilijoutsen B2 </strong>cabins are terraced, and are around 57m<sup>2</sup> sleeping up to two to four people. The cabin has one double room, two single beds in the mezzanine.</p>
<p>End of stay cleaning is included.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>Private Sauna</span></li>
<li><span>Fully equipped kitchen with an electric stove and oven, dishwasher, microwave oven, coffee maker, kettle, toaster, fridge, freezer, iron and washing machine. </span></li>
<li><span>Lounge area </span></li>
<li><span>TV</span></li>
<li><span>Fireplace (firewood included)</span></li>
<li><span>Electric clothes drying cupboard</span></li>
<li><span>Bathroom with shower</span></li>
<li>Cot and high chair can be requested when booking (pay locally)</li>
<li>One linen and towel set included, per person per week</li>
<li>Beds to be made up on arrival</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that not all of the cabins have Wi-Fi access. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
